paragraphs.text:
%md
Performs an L2 regression of the time \\( t_2 \\) value of a call option payoff with respect of a time \\( t_1 \\) value of the underlying, where both are generated off a Black-Scholes model. This gives an approximation of the time \\( t_1 \\) conditional option valuation.

msg.data: Performs an L2 regression of the time \( t_2 \) value of a call option payoff with respect of a time \( t_1 \) value of the underlying, where both are generated off a Black-Scholes model. This gives an approximation of the time \( t_1 \) conditional option valuation.
